logpump (0.1.8) unstable; urgency=low

  * Discard old state if no corresponding files can be found.
  * Ignore sections without pattern in config.
  * Fixes in empty log files handling.
  * New option: -statedir -- use autogenerated state file names if none were
    specified in config.

